</blockquote>

<blockquote>
  <p>T. S. Eliot, ‚ÄúTradition and the Individual Talent‚Äù <a href="https://www.poetryfoundation.org/articles/69400/tradition-and-the-individual-talent">Available here</a><br />
Simon Reynolds, ‚Äúon the roles of the conceptual musician and the conceptualising critic‚Äù, <em>Thinkige Kru</em> (blog). <a href="https://thinkigekru.blogspot.com/2021/11/on-roles-of-conceptual-musician-and.html">Available here</a><br />
